## Description {#details}

Default <a href="/docs/api/namespaces/llvm/#a58b9df85470fc4e2a8066ff6a62e5a34">DomTreeNode</a> traits for NodeT.

The default implementation assume a Function-like NodeT. Can be specialized to support different node types.
